Vulnerability.Title: Format String Bug in Fclicense daemon

cvrf:Acknowledgment.cvrf:Description: Internally discovered and reported by Gwendal Guégniaud of Fortinet Product Security team in the frame of an internal audit of the SSL-VPN component.

cvrf:Note.#text: A use of externally-controlled format string vulnerability [CWE-134] in the Fclicense daemon of FortiOS may allow a remote authenticated attacker to execute arbitrary code or commands via specially crafted requests.
